1
00:00:18,670 --> 00:00:19,760
Saya Zhuge Yue,

2
00:00:20,390 --> 00:00:23,300
tuan muda keempat keluarga Zhuge,
iaitu keluarga bangsawan di negara Yong.

3
00:00:23,300 --> 00:00:26,330
Saya juga Pengurus Pusat Gunung Hijau
yang diwarisi turun-temurun.

4
00:00:25,910 --> 00:00:30,120
[Zhuge Yue,
Pengurus Pusat Gunung Hijau, Negara Yong]

5
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:28,160
Saya setia kepada Maharaja Yong

6
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,690
dan membantu baginda hapuskan pengkhianat.

7
00:00:30,870 --> 00:00:31,550
Yan Xun,

8
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:33,780
[Yan Xun, Putera Yanbei]

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,890
putera Ningrat Penenteram Utara.

10
00:00:33,890 --> 00:00:35,600
Keluarga Yan ditempatkan di Yanbei,

11
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,280
tapi mereka ditakuti
oleh Maharaja Yong,

12
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,280
jadi seluruh keluarga itu dibunuh.

13
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:41,100
Dulu, kami kawan baik.

14
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:42,290
Tapi sekarang,

15
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:43,880
kami dah jadi musuh.

16
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,030
Tuan muda!

17
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,750
Yue Qi!

18
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,520
Tuan,

19
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,520
itu Cik Chu.

20
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,120
Zhuge Yue!

21
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:57,410
[Chu Qiao]

22
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:02,710
Xing Er,

23
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,400
ke tepi.

24
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,240
Zhuge Yue,

25
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:10,400
saya bersalah kepada awak.

26
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,800
Yan Xun,

27
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,630
bunuhlah saya dulu!

28
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,430
Zhuge Yue!

29
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:33,500
Zhuge Yue.

30
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:34,840
Zhuge Yue!

31
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:36,960
Xing Er.

32
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:37,880
Saya di sini.

33
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:41,240
Cepat pergi.

34
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:42,000
Tak.

35
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,800
Kalau nak pergi, kita pergi bersama.

36
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,460
Dulu awak yang lindungi saya.

37
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:47,240
Sekarang,

38
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:50,780
giliran saya pula untuk melindungi awak.

39
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:54,910
Zhuge Yue.

40
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,750
Zhuge Yue,

41
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,600
saya pasti akan bawa awak pergi.

42
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,280
Xing Er,

43
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,120
awak

44
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,030
pasti boleh

45
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:08,150
bawa saya pergi.

46
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,040
Zhuge Yue.

47
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:20,630
Zhuge Yue!

48
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:22,680
Bangunlah!

49
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,720
Bangunlah, awak dah berjanji kepada saya!

50
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,120
Kita kena pergi bersama!

51
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,560
Zhuge Yue!

52
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,480
Jangan tinggalkan saya seorang diri!

53
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:32,920
Tak!

54
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,070
Chu.

55
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,880
Sebenarnya, saya tak pernah berubah.

56
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,040
Cuma awak tak pernah tahu

57
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,750
apa yang saya betul-betul mahukan.

58
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,590
Chu!

59
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:28,650
[REBIRTH]

60
00:07:53,690 --> 00:07:56,230
[Episod 1]

61
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,070
Negara Yong,

62
00:07:58,390 --> 00:07:59,190
Biantang

63
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,270
dan Ximeng,

64
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,990
tiga tempat ini diperintah
secara berasingan.

65
00:08:02,990 --> 00:08:04,190
Biantang kaya dengan sumber
dan rakyatnya ramai,

66
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:06,040
mereka berpuas hati
dengan keadaan sekarang.

67
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:09,300
Cuaca di Ximeng sangat sejuk,
rakyatnya hidup menderita.

68
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:12,270
Pihak negara Yong menjadi kuasa terkuat

69
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:15,670
dengan sistem darjat yang ketat
dan tentera kuat yang gagah.

70
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:18,780
Pada asalnya,
Yanbei ialah negeri naungan negara Yong.

71
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:20,070
Pihak Yanbei dicemburui kerana berjasa

72
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:22,000
lalu bermusuh dengan negara Yong,

73
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:25,880
akhirnya wilayah itu pisahkan diri
dan memerintah sendiri.

74
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:28,000
Tuan muda daripada
keluarga bangsawan negara Yong

75
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,660
suka lihat hamba berlawan
dengan binatang buas

76
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:32,820
dan berhibur dengan memburu hamba.

77
00:08:37,110 --> 00:08:40,010
Anak yatim piatu, Chu Qiao,
menjadi hamba sejak kecil.

78
00:08:40,010 --> 00:08:42,720
Dia sangat benci sistem perhambaan
di negara Yong

79
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,320
lalu bersumpah nak hapuskan perhambaan
dan hentikan peperangan.

80
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,000
Semua ikut!

81
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:59,040
Awak tinggal saja di Pusat Gunung Hijau.

82
00:08:59,040 --> 00:08:59,970
Mulai sekarang,

83
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,870
nama awak ialah Xing Er.

84
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,390
Saya perasan bakatnya yang luar biasa

85
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,520
lalu melantiknya sebagai pengintip.

86
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,240
Zhuge Yue,

87
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:22,320
Xing Er di halaman awak memang berani.

88
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,280
Saya suka dia.

89
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,730
Dia terlalu berani,

90
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:26,030
masih perlu dididik dengan lebih tegas.

91
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,000
Tak perlu didiknya,

92
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,030
beri saya saja.

93
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,080
Tak boleh,

94
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:31,750
baik awak pilih hamba yang lain.

95
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:40,120
Saya kalahkan awak setiap kali,

96
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,030
kenapa awak tak marah kepada saya?

97
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:42,960
Sebab

98
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,240
awak satu-satunya kawan saya.

99
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,960
Bukan pihak Yanbei yang mahu memberontak,

100
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,820
tapi baginda yang harap
pihak Yanbei memberontak.

101
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:52,720
Beta tahu

102
00:09:52,950 --> 00:09:54,670
awak berkawan baik dengan Yan Xun.

103
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:57,000
Beta akan perkenankan Yan Xun kekal hidup

104
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,120
sebagai tanda budi kepada awak.

105
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:01,320
Sama ada dia boleh kekal hidup atau tak,

106
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,870
itu bergantung pada sama ada awak mampu

107
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:05,330
selesaikan perkara ini
untuk beta atau tak.

108
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:07,270
Di atas Platform Sembilan Neraka,

109
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:09,080
Maharaja Yong menitahkan tebusan, Yan Xun,

110
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,960
untuk mengecam kepala ahli keluarganya.

111
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:13,670
Yan Xun menyaksikan
keadaan ahli keluarganya dibakar.

112
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:15,240
Bondanya mangkat dengan tragis.

113
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:18,100
Dia seolah-olah jatuh
ke dalam jurang kehancuran.

114
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:20,480
Yan Xun!

115
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,530
Zhuge Yue!

116
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,730
Kenapa awak mengelakkan saya?

117
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:25,610
Ataupun...

118
00:10:28,290 --> 00:10:30,350
Awak rasa bersalah tentang sesuatu?

119
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,790
Maharaja mahu serang Yanbei,

120
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:39,000
tiada sesiapa yang boleh halang baginda.

121
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:39,870
Baiklah.

122
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,550
Mulai sekarang,

123
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:44,550
awak pewaris Pusat Gunung Hijau

124
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,910
dan menteri negara Yong
yang ada masa depan cerah.

125
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:47,840
Antara saya dengan Chu,

126
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,360
seorang ialah keturunan menteri berdosa
yang dipenjarakan,

127
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,510
seorang lagi ialah

128
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,260
hamba paling hina dalam keluarga Zhuge.

129
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,780
Awak tak perlu datang melawat kami lagi.

130
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,000
Kami pun tak mahu jumpa awak.

131
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,150
Yan Xun,

132
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,910
saya pernah anggap awak
sebagai kawan baik saya,

133
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,840
sebab itu saya menasihati baginda

134
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,720
untuk memadamkan nama awak

135
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,960
daripada senarai ahli keluarga Yan
yang akan dihukum mati.

136
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:12,960
Mengenai Xing Er,

137
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,760
awak sepatutnya tahu.

138
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,720
Bagi saya,

139
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:20,960
dia dah lama bukan lagi hamba
di Pusat Gunung Hijau.

140
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,080
Chu dah lama

141
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:39,270
tiada kaitan dengan awak

142
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,870
dan Pusat Gunung Hijau awak!

143
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,750
Zhuge Yue.

144
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,630
Mulai sekarang, kita berdua

145
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,310
bukan kawan lagi,

146
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,840
kita hanyalah orang asing.

147
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,790
Yan Xun yakin

148
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,510
bahawa semua ini
ialah angkara pihak Pusat Gunung Hijau

149
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:57,240
lalu memutuskan persahabatan
dengan saya sepenuhnya.

150
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,960
Xing Er menyusun semula Tentera Anggun

151
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,220
untuk membantu Yan Xun

152
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,960
lari balik ke Yanbei.

153
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:03,390
Xing Er,

154
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,800
ikut saya balik.

155
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,120
Pemberontakan Yan Xun
tak mungkin akan berjaya.

156
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:07,910
Zhuge Yue,

157
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,200
awak pernah selamatkan nyawa saya,

158
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,570
saya sangat bersyukur.

159
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:12,730
Tapi itu tak bermakna

160
00:12:12,730 --> 00:12:14,720
dendam antara kita boleh terhapus.

161
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,870
Awak tuan muda daripada keluarga bangsawan
yang berkedudukan tinggi,

162
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:19,240
awak langsung tak pedulikan
hidup mati hamba.

163
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,390
Tapi mereka manusia!

164
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:22,390
Mereka ahli keluarga
yang paling saya hargai!

165
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,080
Dulu, awak cederakan Yan Xun
dengan anak panah

166
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:26,120
sehingga menyebabkan kami
gagal larikan diri dari ibu kota

167
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:28,520
dan dipenjarakan selama bertahun-tahun.

168
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:29,630
Kita berdua

169
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,330
memang dah bermusuhan,

170
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,790
kita tak dapat berdamai

171
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,840
dan hal ini tak dapat diubah selamanya.

172
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,510
Xing Er,

173
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,740
awak begitu percayai Yan Xun?

174
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,240
Awak percaya yang dia boleh beri awak
semua yang awak mahukan?

175
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,300
Saya percayainya.

176
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:46,440
Apa yang awak panggil sebagai keadilan,

177
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,170
kesaksamaan

178
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,160
dan cita-cita

179
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,200
tak semudah yang awak fikirkan.

180
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,000
Zhuge Yue,

181
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,910
inilah perbezaan antara kita.

182
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,570
Apa kata kita bertaruh?

183
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:01,150
Bertaruhlah bahawa suatu hari nanti,
di dunia ini,

184
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:03,390
tepuk akan berbalas, alang akan berjawab.

185
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:05,650
Perbezaan darjat pula akan dihapuskan.

186
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:08,320
Yan Xun,

187
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,180
awak dah bersedia?

188
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,790
Selepas saat ini,

189
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,870
kita takkan ada peluang
untuk patah balik lagi.

190
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:16,550
Selepas menamatkan semua ini,

191
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,150
mari kita kembali ke Yanbei.

192
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:20,270
Saya pernah berjanji kepada awak

193
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,480
untuk mengembalikan keamanan
kepada dunia ini.

194
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:25,280
Balas dendam
demi roh-roh Yanbei yang terkorban!

195
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:30,750
Mereka ingin membentuk dunia luas

196
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,960
yang rakyatnya hidup bebas
dan tiada perbezaan darjat.

197
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,240
Namun, hati Yan Xun

198
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,440
dah lama ditenggelami dendam kesumat.

199
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,440
Dia mempergunakan perasaan saya
terhadap Xing Er

200
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,700
untuk mengumpan saya pergi ke tasik ais.

201
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,520
Apabila Xing Er sedar semua ini,

202
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,880
semuanya dah terlambat.

203
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:47,840
Yan Xun,

204
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,720
bunuhlah saya dulu!

205
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,270
Zhuge Yue,

206
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,490
saya bersalah kepada awak.

207
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,510
Tak!

208
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,270
Cik Chu, cik dah sedar.

209
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:25,450
[Su, gadis suruhan, Yanbei]

210
00:14:24,370 --> 00:14:25,770
Demam awak pun dah kebah.

211
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:28,240
Awak siapa?

212
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,510
Di mana sini?

213
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:34,120
Cik Chu.

214
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,630
Cik masih tak ingat apa-apa?

215
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,390
Cik Chu?

216
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:45,200
Peperangan ini dah berlarutan

217
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,660
selama hampir tiga bulan.

218
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:49,510
Kekuatan Tentera Yong
tak setanding dengan pihak Yanbei,

219
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:51,200
tapi Yanbei sangat sejuk.

220
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:52,480
Iklim di sana dan bekalan makanan mereka

221
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,720
lebih sesuai untuk perang jangka panjang
berbanding dengan kita.

222
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,360
Zhao Che, putera ketujuh
yang memimpin tentera itu

223
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,360
seorang yang tekal.

224
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,960
Jika dia terus melanjutkan peperangan ini
dengan kita,

225
00:14:57,400 --> 00:15:00,840
[Panglima Shi Yan,
Komander Tentera Helang Hitam, Yanbei]

226
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,750
saya bimbang Panglima Huan
dan Tentera Helang Hitam

227
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:03,000
tak dapat bertahan lagi.

228
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,320
Zhao Che enggan kerahkan semua tenteranya

229
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,440
kerana mahu meletihkan tentera kita

230
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:08,600
dan memaksa kita berundur.

231
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,930
Jika kita berputus asa sekarang,

232
00:15:08,660 --> 00:15:12,170
[Panglima Cheng Yuan,
Leftenan Tentera Helang Hitam, Yanbei]

233
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,080
maka sia-sialah segala usaha kita.

234
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:15,390
Tuanku,

235
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:18,630
negara Yong dah kehilangan
lima buah kota berturut-turut.

236
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,150
Penasihat tentera mereka, Zhuge Yue,

237
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,480
pula dah mati di Yanbei.

238
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,330
Kalau kita terlalu mendesak,

239
00:15:23,390 --> 00:15:25,750
patik bimbang kedua-dua pihak
akan rugi akhirnya.

240
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,950
Biarpun kita menang,

241
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:28,240
bagi Yanbei,

242
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:30,270
kita tetap perlu tanggung
pengorbanan yang besar.

243
00:15:30,270 --> 00:15:32,330
Mohon tuanku pertimbangkan hal ini.

244
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,270
Tuanku,

245
00:15:33,670 --> 00:15:34,750
Cik Chu dah sedar.

246
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:39,430
Chu, awak dah sedar.

247
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,100
Tabib,

248
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:43,960
cepat periksa keadaan maharani.

249
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,290
Junjung titah, tuanku.

250
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:53,440
Yang Teramat Mulia
pernah teringat apa-apa?

251
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,100
Kenapa dia tak ingat apa-apa?

252
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:03,050
Demam maharani belum kebah sepenuhnya,

253
00:16:03,050 --> 00:16:04,250
beliau pun tak sedar.

254
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,750
Mungkin ini hanya keadaan sementara,

255
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:08,190
tapi mungkin juga ini disebabkan
oleh kecederaan luaran.

256
00:16:08,190 --> 00:16:09,190
Semua ini

257
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,000
baru dapat diketahui selepas beliau

258
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,200
sedar sepenuhnya.

259
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:14,750
Seingat saya,

260
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:17,890
awak tabib.

261
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,360
Perkara lain...

262
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,150
Saya bermimpi.

263
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:31,490
Saya bermimpi saya berada
di dalam tasik ais.

264
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:34,880
Saya terperangkap di dasar tasik ais itu,

265
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,330
tak dapat bernafas.

266
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,810
Tiga bulan dah berlalu,

267
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,790
tapi kenapa dia hanya sedar dua kali?

268
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:51,270
Setiap kali, dia mengigau

269
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:53,370
dan tak ingat apa-apa pun.

270
00:16:53,690 --> 00:16:54,300
Tuanku,

271
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,930
jangan terlalu risau.

272
00:16:56,190 --> 00:16:58,720
Selepas maharani jatuh ke dalam tasik ais,
beliau demam panas beberapa hari.

273
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,120
Sekarang, penyakit dingin
di dalam tubuh beliau

274
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,580
belum hilang sepenuhnya.

275
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:03,630
Beliau boleh bercakap
dan bergerak bebas sekarang,

276
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:05,480
ini dah dikira rahmat dalam musibah.

277
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,670
Buat masa ini,
beliau perlu berehat secukupnya.

278
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:10,730
Mengenai hal bila beliau
akan teringat kisah lalunya,

279
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,750
janganlah tergesa-gesa.

280
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,980
Tuanku boleh berbual dengan maharani

281
00:17:14,980 --> 00:17:16,460
tentang kisah lalu.

282
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,310
Cara ini

283
00:17:17,550 --> 00:17:19,880
dapat membantu beliau pulihkan ingatan.

284
00:17:20,109 --> 00:17:20,829
Awak kata,

285
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:23,109
saya maharani?

286
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,550
Ya,

287
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:38,050
awak bakal maharani beta.

288
00:17:38,350 --> 00:17:40,480
Sebelum awak jatuh ke dalam tasik ais,

289
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,440
kita hampir berkahwin.

290
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,640
Berkahwin?

291
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:55,030
Biar saya bawa awak pergi tengok sesuatu.

292
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:08,510
Chu,

293
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:12,040
ini baju pengantin
yang saya sediakan untuk awak.

294
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,840
Kita sehidup semati.

295
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,810
Dah lama kita berjanji untuk bersama.

296
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,110
Tiga bulan lalu,

297
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,040
kalau penjahat negara Yong

298
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,260
tak menyelinap masuk ke wilayah saya

299
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:26,670
semasa perkahwinan kita

300
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:27,950
untuk membunuh kita,

301
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,490
awak dah pun menjadi

302
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,210
Maharani Yanbei saya yang sah.

303
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,610
Negara Yong?

304
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:36,830
Negara Yong.

305
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:38,730
Chu, awak masih ingat tak?

306
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,840
Semasa saya masih muda,

307
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,590
saya dipaksa menjadi tebusan
di kota Zhenhuang, negara Yong.

308
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:47,390
Kemudian, kami berkenalan
di Pusat Gunung Hijau.

309
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:50,190
Lepas itu,
keluarga saya ditimpa malapetaka.

310
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:52,660
Awaklah

311
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:57,040
yang melindungi saya
agar saya dapat kekal hidup.

312
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:04,030
Yan Shicheng, Ningrat Penenteram Utara,

313
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:05,430
memiliki tentera demi kepentingan diri!

314
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:07,990
Dia menghina dunia, menipu maharaja

315
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,510
dan mengelirukan rakyat,

316
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:12,680
malah kerahkan Tentera Yan secara haram
untuk mencetuskan pemberontakan!

317
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:15,400
Niatnya untuk menderhaka
diketahui semua orang!

318
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:17,000
Mujurlah maharaja kita arif

319
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,660
dan diberkati oleh tuhan.

320
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,680
Pemberontakan di Yanbei dah diselesaikan,

321
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,700
keluarga Yan yang mengkhianat
dah dihapuskan!

322
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:24,730
Memandangkan Yan Xun dibesarkan
di kota Zhenhuang

323
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:25,950
dan tak terlibat dalam pemberontakan,

324
00:19:25,950 --> 00:19:28,340
kini dia dititahkan untuk
mengecam kepala penjenayah

325
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:28,010
[Zhuge Huai, Keluarga Zhuge, Negara Yong]

326
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:30,270
agar dosanya diampunkan.

327
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:46,730
Pemerintah Yanbei
yang warisi tanah kurniaan,

328
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,740
cucu ke-24 Maharaja Pei Luo,

329
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,640
papan roh ke-576

330
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:55,170
di Tokong Leluhur Kemuliaan,
Istana Rezeki,

331
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:57,880
Marsyal Agung
Tentera Barat Laut negara Yong,

332
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,720
Raja Penstabil Barat dari Yanbei,

333
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,790
Yan Shicheng!

334
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:03,960
Dia dipancung
pada tanggal 14 bulan empat

335
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,930
di Dataran Guruh Api, Yanbei.

336
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:11,610
Zhuge Huai, saya akan bunuh awak!

337
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:15,500
Yan Ting, putera sulung Yan Shicheng,
Raja Penstabil Barat, Yanbei!

338
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,510
Pada tanggal 14 bulan empat,

339
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:21,440
dia dipancung di kota Xunlie, Yanbei.

340
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:23,280
Nama dah siap diumumkan.

341
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:26,510
Putera Yan, sila cam penjenayah!

342
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,200
Terima titah itu.

343
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,500
Yan Xun,

344
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,880
cepat terima titah.

345
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,130
Naiklah untuk melihat kepala ayah

346
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,000
dan adik-beradik awak.

347
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:09,770
Anak penderhaka, Yan Xun, ingkar titah!

348
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:11,630
Tangkap dia!

349
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:17,120
Yan Xun!

350
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,200
Tak!

351
00:21:52,510 --> 00:21:54,000
Yan Xun, awak bodoh!

352
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,750
Awak nak cari mati?

353
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,250
Tak perlu cam penjenayah lagi.

354
00:22:16,790 --> 00:22:18,450
Tangkap penjenayah, Yan Xun!

355
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:20,790
Zhuge Yue,

356
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,550
titah yang dihantar dari kota Zhenhuang

357
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:24,790
adalah untuk dia memeriksa mayat.

358
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,480
Macam boleh selesaikan hal ini
secara sambil lewa?

359
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,510
Awak buat macam ini,

360
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:29,590
tak takut maharaja akan salahkan awak?

361
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:31,550
Sama ada baginda akan salahkan saya
atau tak,

362
00:22:31,550 --> 00:22:32,810
ini bukan urusan awak.

363
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,650
Awak berkeras nak membela dia,

364
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:37,350
tapi itu terpulanglah
sama ada dia hargainya atau tak.

365
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:37,960
Pengawal!

366
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:43,080
Orang keji dari Yanbei,

367
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:44,750
saya nak awak tengok

368
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:50,420
keadaan ahli keluarga
dan saudara-mara awak dibakar menjadi abu!

369
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:53,200
Yan Xun,

370
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:55,110
awak nak periksa atau tak?

371
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:57,790
Zhuge Huai!

372
00:22:58,070 --> 00:22:59,420
Zhuge Huai, saya akan bunuh awak!

373
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:00,790
Saya akan bunuh awak!

374
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,150
Biar saya yang periksa!

375
00:23:28,940 --> 00:23:32,240
[Bai Sheng,
Isteri Ningrat Penenteram Utara]

376
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:31,750
Xun.

377
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,200
Bonda.

378
00:23:45,670 --> 00:23:46,540
Xun,

379
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:48,550
jangan menangis.

380
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,680
Anak-anak keluarga Yan

381
00:23:52,370 --> 00:23:54,570
hanya akan berdarah, takkan menangis.

382
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:55,440
Bonda,

383
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:58,060
apa yang berlaku sebenarnya?

384
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,860
Anakanda percayai ayahanda tak?

385
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:02,020
Anakanda percaya.

386
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,720
Di dunia ini,

387
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:05,830
tak semua punca hal

388
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,480
dapat dijelaskan.

389
00:24:11,410 --> 00:24:12,650
Merekakah?

390
00:24:18,350 --> 00:24:20,160
Mereka yang menganiaya Yanbei?

391
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:21,510
Xun.

392
00:24:23,540 --> 00:24:24,430
Bangunlah.

393
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,620
Biar saya yang periksa mayat!

394
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,970
Semua orang di atas sana

395
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,240
ialah suami saya,

396
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:38,680
putera saya,

397
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:40,070
puteri saya

398
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,400
dan ahli keluarga saya.

399
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:44,880
Saya percaya, di dunia ini,

400
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:47,160
tiada sesiapa
yang lebih layak buat hal ini

401
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,350
daripada saya!

402
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,960
Maharaja menitahkan Yan Xun

403
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,070
untuk memeriksa pengenalan penjenayah.

404
00:24:52,070 --> 00:24:54,030
Takkanlah awak nak mengingkari titah?

405
00:24:54,030 --> 00:24:54,880
Pengawal!

406
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:57,540
Tangkap orang yang ingkar titah ini!

407
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,650
Seluruh keluarga Yan dah mati.

408
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:03,530
Kenapa hanya Maharani Yan
yang masih hidup?

409
00:25:04,290 --> 00:25:05,820
Tuanku pernah menitahkan,

410
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:08,720
selagi Maharani Yan
tak tinggalkan kota Zhenhuang,

411
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:11,380
tiada sesiapa pun
yang boleh cederakan beliau.

412
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:12,350
Zhuge Huai,

413
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,860
takkanlah awak nak mengingkari titah juga?

414
00:25:14,860 --> 00:25:15,320
Saya...

415
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:19,830
Berundur.

416
00:25:28,650 --> 00:25:29,370
Bonda.

417
00:25:50,630 --> 00:25:52,190
Ini suami saya.

418
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:56,120
Pemerintah Yanbei
yang warisi tanah kurniaan,

419
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:57,920
Maharaja Yanbei, Yan Shicheng!

420
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,160
Dalam peperangan di Benteng Kuda Putih,

421
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,750
300 ribu Tentera Quanrong
serbu masuk ke benteng!

422
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:05,640
Shicheng mengetuai tenteranya
bertolak dari Yanbei!

423
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,310
Mereka bertarung selama tujuh hari
tujuh malam tanpa henti!

424
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:11,910
Dia pimpin tentera dan selamatkan
negara Yong daripada bahaya!

425
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:14,510
Maharaja kamu bersumpah ketika itu

426
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,360
yang negara Yong dan Yanbei

427
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:19,570
akan jadi pemerintah dan menteri yang
takkan tinggalkan masing-masing selamanya!

428
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:22,030
Pada masa itu,
kebanyakan orang antara kamu

429
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,880
pun ada di sana.

430
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,550
Ini putera saya.

431
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:30,200
Tahun ini, dia berumur 21 tahun.

432
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,550
Dia menyertai tentera pada umur 13 tahun,

433
00:26:32,550 --> 00:26:34,880
bermula sebagai tentera berpangkat rendah!

434
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,790
Dalam lapan tahun,

435
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:38,240
dia dah menangkis serangan Quanrong
sebanyak 67 kali

436
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,700
dan mencapai banyak jasa dalam peperangan!

437
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:42,430
Pada tanggal 14 bulan empat,

438
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:44,440
di kota Xunlie,

439
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,730
dia mangkat dipijak kuda!

440
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,720
Ini puteri saya!

441
00:26:58,240 --> 00:26:59,840
Pada tanggal 16 bulan empat,

442
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:03,960
dia menunggang kuda
untuk menyelamatkan bondanya yang diculik.

443
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:06,220
Ketika melalui Tasik Hong di Sungai Wei,

444
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:09,800
dia dibunuh dalam kehuru-haraan tentera!

445
00:27:14,350 --> 00:27:17,240
Mereka ialah pahlawan Yanbei!

446
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,590
Zhuge Huai,

447
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,880
laksanakan hukuman.

448
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:24,030
Laksanakan hukuman!

449
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:36,300
Jangan!

450
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,830
Jangan!

451
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:42,970
Yan Xun!

452
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,510
Yan Xun!

453
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,400
Yan Xun!

454
00:27:52,690 --> 00:27:53,210
Tak!

455
00:27:54,050 --> 00:27:54,620
Tak!

456
00:27:57,170 --> 00:27:57,850
Yan Xun!

457
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,630
Tolong lepaskan putera saya.

458
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,790
Bonda!

459
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,110
Bonda!

460
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:32,640
Bonda!

461
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,900
Kenapa bonda buat begini?

462
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:39,590
Ayahanda dah tiada.

463
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,920
Kanda pun dah tiada.

464
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,920
Semua ahli keluarga dah tiada.

465
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:49,230
Bonda pun nak tinggalkan Xun?

466
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:55,070
Xu... Xun.

467
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,810
Berjanji kepada bonda.

468
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:00,450
Anakanda mesti terus hidup.

469
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,600
Walaupun hidup lebih seksa
daripada mangkat,

470
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:08,460
anakanda tetap mesti terus hidup.

471
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:21,720
Bonda!

